ServiceAssistant

agents:
	humans: ServiceUser
	robots: Robot
locations: room7002, elevator, room3201
resources: basket, object

Robot:

1: moveTo room7002
2-3: waitForHuman ServiceUser until true
4: moveTo elevator
5-6: askForHumanAssistance elevatorRide until true
7: moveInsideElevator
8-9: askForHumanAssistance floorReached until true
10: moveOutsideElevator
11: moveTo room3201
12: waitForHuman ServiceUser until true
13: serviceGoalAccomplished

ServiceUser:

1-4: moveTo room7002
5-6: putObjectInBasket
7: moveTo elevator
8-9: rideElevator room3201 until true
10: moveTo room3201
11-12: collectObjectAndConfirmServiceCompletion
